TI  - Changing concepts in breast cancer.
PG  - 609-10
FAU - Leis, H P
AU  - Leis HP
LA  - eng
PT  - Journal Article
PL  - Italy
TA  - Int Surg
JT  - International surgery
JID - 0043524
SB  - IM
MH  - Adult
MH  - Age Factors
MH  - Aged
MH  - Breast Neoplasms/diagnostic imaging/genetics/surgery/*therapy
MH  - Female
MH  - Humans
